WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 35=

01:54.270 --> 01:55.500
So, Yan Ke rebelled.

02:00.340 --> 02:01.830
The Void is still in turmoil.

02:03.030 --> 02:04.323
So, you'll be leaving again soon?

02:06.700 --> 02:07.540
That's right.

02:10.620 --> 02:11.670
How long will it be?

02:13.270 --> 02:14.300
Will it be years

02:14.740 --> 02:15.860
or even over a decade?

02:18.070 --> 02:19.580
As for the Void, it depends.

02:20.020 --> 02:21.420
Sometimes, it's a few years;

02:21.700 --> 02:23.420
sometimes, it's over a decade.

02:29.002 --> 02:30.056
How long will it take you?

02:32.580 --> 02:33.420
Me?

02:38.670 --> 02:39.510
About half a year.

03:12.270 --> 03:13.180
Foxy?

03:27.790 --> 03:28.630
Half a year?

03:30.270 --> 03:31.900
You'll miss Luozhou's bloom.

03:35.460 --> 03:36.300
Luozhou's peonies

03:36.300 --> 03:37.140
are the most famous.

03:38.390 --> 03:39.270
I planned to take you

03:39.580 --> 03:40.420
to see peonies

03:41.700 --> 03:42.900
once they bloom

03:42.900 --> 03:43.740
next spring.

03:44.579 --> 03:45.540
The breeze will be soft;

03:46.658 --> 03:47.719
the flowers will be sweet.

03:49.140 --> 03:49.990
If you like the wind,

03:50.550 --> 03:51.390
we can ride horses

03:51.460 --> 03:52.502
through the flower fields.

03:54.110 --> 03:54.950
Foxy,

03:55.550 --> 03:56.420
listen to yourself.

03:56.420 --> 03:57.550
How many things did you name?

03:58.140 --> 04:00.550
Sight, touch, and smell.

04:00.860 --> 04:02.110
You want to give me all of them?

04:02.266 --> 04:03.140
That's not impossible.

04:03.300 --> 04:04.140
Duan Xu,

04:04.390 --> 04:05.856
ever since Fengyi taught you

04:05.867 --> 04:06.960
how to swap the five senses,

04:07.110 --> 04:08.350
you've grown restrained.

04:09.900 --> 04:11.350
If you have only one sensation,

04:12.580 --> 04:13.620
you'd have no way

04:14.550 --> 04:15.900
to feel all things in this world.

05:04.990 --> 05:06.030
I don't want to go back.

05:08.300 --> 05:09.860
I want to go to your Void tomorrow

05:12.380 --> 05:13.230
and build you

05:13.230 --> 05:14.180
another splendid palace.

05:15.940 --> 05:17.380
A splendid palace?

05:18.620 --> 05:19.470
Then,

05:20.380 --> 05:21.550
should we also build

05:21.550 --> 05:22.820
a peacock that fans its tail?

05:26.230 --> 05:27.730
The other spirits can't see it anyway.

05:28.820 --> 05:29.660
Only I

05:30.550 --> 05:31.390
would have

05:31.706 --> 05:32.752
such a palace in the Void.

05:33.433 --> 05:34.577
Wouldn't that be delightful?

05:35.768 --> 05:37.486
Besides, once I give you
my sense of color,

05:37.497 --> 05:38.697
you'll be able to see colors.

05:39.570 --> 05:41.097
Just thinking of it feels so striking.

05:42.156 --> 05:43.443
It'll also help you know colors.

05:45.110 --> 05:46.423
I still think it won't look good.

05:51.670 --> 05:53.110
I'll make sure it's beautiful.

06:27.380 --> 06:29.220
(Weizhou)

06:30.350 --> 06:31.740
At last, we've taken Weizhou.

06:32.219 --> 06:33.166
Where do we strike next?

06:33.420 --> 06:34.260
Next,

06:34.420 --> 06:35.710
we should throw all our strength

06:35.710 --> 06:36.710
into taking Youzhou.

06:36.710 --> 06:38.260
- Yes, Youzhou.
- Yes, Youzhou.

06:38.260 --> 06:39.990
His Majesty's decree has arrived.

06:45.350 --> 06:46.790
By His Majesty's decree,

06:46.790 --> 06:49.620
Duan Xu has beaten greater odds

06:49.820 --> 06:52.380
and won back Weizhou for Great Liang.

06:52.910 --> 06:53.940
He is hereby appointed

06:54.110 --> 06:55.590
Grand Marshal of All

06:55.790 --> 06:57.060
to command the Three Armies.

06:57.380 --> 06:58.710
Thus decreed.

07:03.670 --> 07:04.623
Thank you, Your Majesty.

07:07.300 --> 07:08.230
Congrats, Marshal Duan.

07:11.910 --> 07:12.790
Good.

07:12.790 --> 07:13.710
Very good.

07:13.710 --> 07:14.550
Truly excellent.

07:16.820 --> 07:18.353
- You've been promoted.
- From now on,

07:18.790 --> 07:20.860
we can't call you General Duan.

07:21.500 --> 07:23.180
From now on, we should call you

07:23.500 --> 07:24.740
Marshal Duan.

07:24.940 --> 07:27.060
- Marshal Duan.
- Marshal Duan.

07:31.590 --> 07:33.060
If Han

07:33.670 --> 07:35.180
were still here,

07:38.260 --> 07:39.790
that would be even better.

07:40.740 --> 07:41.580
Even better.

07:49.420 --> 07:50.260
Xu.

07:53.380 --> 07:54.220
Xu,

07:54.470 --> 07:55.910
are you going to see Xiaoxiao?

07:57.330 --> 07:58.365
Lately, you've gathered

07:58.376 --> 07:59.180
all the goodies

07:59.180 --> 08:00.020
from the camp.

08:00.260 --> 08:01.750
It must all be for Xiaoxiao.

08:03.350 --> 08:04.190
You're a sharp one.

08:05.180 --> 08:06.420
Xu, you're so unfair.

08:08.510 --> 08:09.743
Why are you still following me?

08:09.889 --> 08:10.866
Why aren't you drilling?

08:11.150 --> 08:11.990
Xu,

08:11.990 --> 08:12.840
it's been so long

08:12.860 --> 08:13.886
since I last saw Xiaoxiao.

08:14.260 --> 08:15.910
You can't keep her all to yourself.

08:37.833 --> 08:39.140
I still recall the rich fragrance

08:39.140 --> 08:40.260
of Nü'erhong.

09:08.860 --> 09:09.700
Xiaoxiao.

09:12.453 --> 09:13.479
Xu picked this on the way.

09:13.710 --> 09:14.550
It's for you.

09:24.470 --> 09:25.636
You can finally taste things,

09:26.070 --> 09:27.350
but the camp has little to offer.

09:27.530 --> 09:28.610
The ingredients are plain.

09:30.140 --> 09:31.620
This camellia honey can be sipped.

09:31.860 --> 09:32.710
It's sweet.

09:32.900 --> 09:33.740
Give it a try.

09:41.200 --> 09:42.070
It's light and sweet,

09:42.070 --> 09:42.910
with a floral note.

09:43.069 --> 09:44.382
Even better than a sugar figurine.

09:45.830 --> 09:46.900
Now, try these as well.

09:54.780 --> 09:56.540
The fresh sweetness of nectar lingered.

09:56.900 --> 09:57.740
Even these dishes

09:57.900 --> 09:59.020
taste much sweeter now.

09:59.710 --> 10:00.590
Xiaoxiao,

10:00.590 --> 10:01.990
try my favorite meat pie too.

10:13.140 --> 10:14.020
It's so good.

10:14.567 --> 10:15.960
No wonder you eat eight at a meal.

10:46.020 --> 10:46.860
Xiaoxiao,

10:47.070 --> 10:47.950
you can't eat anymore.

10:48.350 --> 10:49.740
You've already had ten.

10:52.590 --> 10:53.430
Then I'll stop.

10:54.110 --> 10:55.430
It's all gone already.

11:20.190 --> 11:21.030
Great Ancestor,

11:22.780 --> 11:23.950
you're feasting in style,

11:23.950 --> 11:25.350
and you did not invite me?

11:26.470 --> 11:27.470
I was working hard

11:28.230 --> 11:29.916
on blessing talismans
on the battlefield,

11:30.190 --> 11:31.380
while you were relaxing here.

11:31.590 --> 11:32.540
Prophet Hejia, thanks

11:32.540 --> 11:33.380
for your hard work.

11:33.620 --> 11:34.540
It's not hard at all.

11:34.540 --> 11:35.380
He enjoyed himself.

11:36.380 --> 11:37.230
Perfect timing.

11:37.316 --> 11:38.602
I want iced fermented rice wine.

11:45.190 --> 11:46.710
Great Ancestor knows how to enjoy life.

11:47.140 --> 11:48.500
You boss me around once I arrive.

11:50.470 --> 11:51.380
Who'd have thought

11:51.780 --> 11:52.660
that one day,

11:53.020 --> 11:54.500
I'd be sharing wine

11:54.780 --> 11:55.990
with Great Ancestor?

11:56.540 --> 11:57.660
Another joy

11:58.140 --> 11:58.990
in the Mortal World.

11:59.860 --> 12:00.700
Still,

12:02.500 --> 12:04.950
Marshal Duan swapped
the five senses now.

12:05.500 --> 12:07.070
Aren't you worried about the battle?

12:10.523 --> 12:11.582
The war has eased for now.

12:11.990 --> 12:13.350
I only changed my sense of taste.

12:13.740 --> 12:14.580
It won't matter.

12:15.310 --> 12:16.740
Prophet Hejia, rest easy.

12:17.070 --> 12:18.350
With Xu's capability,

12:18.593 --> 12:20.039
losing her sense of taste is nothing.

12:20.103 --> 12:21.350
Even if he lost his five senses,

12:21.350 --> 12:22.710
he could still crush the enemy.

12:24.660 --> 12:25.500
Xiaoxiao,

12:25.800 --> 12:26.660
you have no idea

12:26.660 --> 12:27.900
how terrifying Xu is,

12:28.350 --> 12:29.740
especially when he trained me.

12:30.190 --> 12:31.900
I truly thought he was tormenting me.

12:34.180 --> 12:35.020
Well done.

12:35.020 --> 12:35.950
Only then will he learn.

12:41.620 --> 12:42.460
Great Ancestor…

12:43.070 --> 12:43.910
Move aside.

12:44.500 --> 12:45.340
Move aside.

12:46.540 --> 12:47.380
Move aside.

13:07.706 --> 13:08.740
I must return to the Void.

13:09.830 --> 13:10.900
If danger finds you,

13:11.380 --> 13:12.350
be sure to call for me.

13:18.500 --> 13:19.590
Keep yourself safe too.

13:21.350 --> 13:22.190
Remember to miss me.

13:30.070 --> 13:30.910
Don't worry.

13:31.590 --> 13:32.710
Great Ancestor won't lose.

13:41.990 --> 13:42.830
Xu.

13:43.020 --> 13:43.860
Xu, what's wrong?

13:45.780 --> 13:46.620
Xu.

14:20.140 --> 14:20.980
Chenying,

14:23.350 --> 14:24.590
I'm fine for now.

14:26.110 --> 14:26.950
Leave us.

14:28.020 --> 14:29.070
Don't tell anyone about me

14:30.500 --> 14:31.830
coughing up blood.

14:32.590 --> 14:33.800
- But, Xu...
- Go.

14:35.740 --> 14:36.580
I'm ordering you.

14:51.290 --> 14:53.010
You traded your senses
with Great Ancestor,

14:53.470 --> 14:55.110
so you suffer such agonizing backlash.

14:56.380 --> 14:57.860
Now, your senses are fading,

14:58.070 --> 14:59.350
and your body is failing fast.

14:59.860 --> 15:00.700
If this continues,

15:01.380 --> 15:02.220
you won't be granted

15:03.660 --> 15:04.710
a peaceful old age.

15:09.380 --> 15:10.220
It's all right.

15:12.590 --> 15:13.430
It's enough already.

15:16.500 --> 15:17.660
Prophet Hejia,

15:19.860 --> 15:20.780
please don't tell Simu

15:20.780 --> 15:21.620
about this.

15:24.230 --> 15:25.260
There is still no way

15:25.260 --> 15:26.140
to cure it for now,

15:26.350 --> 15:27.710
but if you stop swapping

15:27.710 --> 15:28.620
the five senses,

15:29.230 --> 15:30.070
perhaps

15:30.230 --> 15:31.660
the illness can be held for now.

15:32.190 --> 15:33.740
I have long known of this harm.

15:37.710 --> 15:38.550
This is why I remain

15:38.560 --> 15:39.590
by her side.

15:41.990 --> 15:42.830
There is little

15:42.840 --> 15:43.710
I can do for her.

15:45.540 --> 15:46.780
If I can't even do this,

15:48.430 --> 15:49.380
what else can I do?

15:49.710 --> 15:51.190
But you are doing this by spending

15:51.190 --> 15:52.620
your health and your lifespan.

15:52.900 --> 15:54.110
Would she be pleased?

15:57.860 --> 15:59.350
The days I can stay by her side

15:59.350 --> 16:00.190
have never been many.

16:05.780 --> 16:07.710
Perhaps I will end up blurring

16:10.500 --> 16:11.620
and fade away

16:12.540 --> 16:13.380
just like

16:14.990 --> 16:15.830
all her other lovers.

16:18.590 --> 16:19.740
But exchanging the senses

16:19.740 --> 16:21.140
was unique to her.

16:23.590 --> 16:24.470
By my side,

16:27.830 --> 16:28.710
she once possessed

16:28.710 --> 16:29.740
a lively world.

16:31.950 --> 16:33.310
I only hope that she can be happy,

16:35.660 --> 16:37.350
and that this happiness

16:40.446 --> 16:41.499
will make her remember me.

16:48.140 --> 16:49.350
I have felt the world

16:49.350 --> 16:50.500
she lives in every day.

16:52.830 --> 16:53.900
It's too cold and lonely.

16:55.860 --> 16:57.190
I don't want that for her.

17:04.390 --> 17:05.470
You're a madman.

17:07.740 --> 17:08.670
No wonder Great Ancestor

17:08.670 --> 17:09.630
fell for you.

17:12.190 --> 17:13.030
Enough.

17:14.190 --> 17:15.470
I will find a way to save you.

17:17.500 --> 17:19.100
There's no spiritual medicine here.

17:19.196 --> 17:20.342
I'll return to Nandu at once.

17:21.780 --> 17:22.620
In that case,

17:23.910 --> 17:25.260
I'll leave it to you.

17:36.630 --> 17:37.470
Xu, the Chong forces

17:37.592 --> 17:38.562
strike the western front.

17:38.573 --> 17:39.555
Their assault is fierce.

17:39.566 --> 17:40.886
Qingsheng sent for aid.

17:45.740 --> 17:46.580
Gather the troops.

17:47.340 --> 17:48.180
Yes.

18:15.780 --> 18:17.100
The Liang Army is advancing fast.

18:17.470 --> 18:18.580
Weizhou has already fallen.

18:19.230 --> 18:20.870
We can't let Duan Xu live on.

18:31.630 --> 18:33.150
If he dies just like this,

18:34.580 --> 18:36.230
it would be letting him off too easily.

19:08.990 --> 19:10.670
Those Chong forces under poison again.

19:11.020 --> 19:11.776
If not for them,

19:11.787 --> 19:12.820
we'd never be surrounded.

19:12.820 --> 19:13.823
Hold on a little longer.

19:13.990 --> 19:15.630
Xia can break out with the host.

19:42.820 --> 19:43.660
Xu!

19:44.540 --> 19:45.950
Xu, are you alright?

19:57.430 --> 19:58.270
Xu!

20:01.300 --> 20:02.140
Xu!

20:02.670 --> 20:03.510
What happened to you?

20:03.780 --> 20:04.620
Xu!

20:04.910 --> 20:05.750
Guards!

20:05.910 --> 20:07.060
Take Marshal Duan back

20:07.780 --> 20:09.100
as soon as possible!

20:09.370 --> 20:10.230
- Yes!
- Yes!

20:10.230 --> 20:11.070
Xu!

20:11.340 --> 20:12.300
Xu, hang in there.

20:12.300 --> 20:13.170
Marshal Duan!

20:13.190 --> 20:14.500
Stay with us, Xu!

20:14.870 --> 20:15.710
Marshal Duan!

20:16.390 --> 20:17.640
After you proved

20:17.651 --> 20:18.784
Yan Ke's crimes to everyone,

20:19.100 --> 20:21.020
all the Lords pledged loyalty at once.

20:21.340 --> 20:22.300
You cleared

20:22.300 --> 20:23.630
quite a few old cases.

20:24.473 --> 20:25.713
You're always at Xuling Temple

20:25.724 --> 20:26.710
or the Sovereign's Hall.

20:26.710 --> 20:27.550
I'm so bored

20:27.560 --> 20:28.410
by your side.

20:28.780 --> 20:30.470
You insisted on following me.

20:31.060 --> 20:31.950
What?

20:31.950 --> 20:33.216
You want to read memorials too?

20:36.990 --> 20:37.830
I can give you a few.

20:38.060 --> 20:38.990
You can lend me a hand.

20:42.100 --> 20:43.163
Why read

20:43.174 --> 20:44.300
all that long-winded stuff?

20:45.390 --> 20:46.939
When you were the Lord of Qiling Temple,

20:46.950 --> 20:48.005
Yan Ke handled the reports

20:48.016 --> 20:48.773
for you, didn't he?

20:48.910 --> 20:50.550
No wonder you'd be fooled and not know.

21:18.479 --> 21:19.470
I think you're doing this

21:19.470 --> 21:20.646
to get back at me on purpose.

21:28.630 --> 21:30.580
Bai Sanxing has quite a fierce temper,

21:31.150 --> 21:32.020
but when facing you,

21:32.390 --> 21:34.190
he just can't vent his anger.

21:34.780 --> 21:35.630
He deserves it.

21:38.190 --> 21:39.230
If the one controlling him

21:39.230 --> 21:40.710
were someone else,

21:41.150 --> 21:42.190
with his temper,

21:42.430 --> 21:44.060
he'd choose annihilation over bowing.

21:53.340 --> 21:54.710
Let's talk about your young lover.

21:55.820 --> 21:57.020
I've heard that lately,

21:57.020 --> 21:58.740
he's famed for battle
in the Mortal World.

21:59.150 --> 22:00.670
Why not have him come to the Void?

22:01.470 --> 22:03.150
Then you two needn't live apart.

22:04.430 --> 22:05.820
He has his battles to fight,

22:06.470 --> 22:07.630
and I have mine.

22:08.230 --> 22:09.070
Lady Jiang Ai,

22:09.820 --> 22:11.340
let's drag him into this.

22:11.640 --> 22:12.500
What's wrong?

22:12.500 --> 22:13.340
You miss him?

22:16.710 --> 22:17.550
Simu,

22:18.100 --> 22:18.940
what is it?

22:23.910 --> 22:25.150
I can't quite put it into words.

22:26.870 --> 22:27.820
Lately, I've found

22:27.820 --> 22:28.670
something off.

22:35.390 --> 22:36.340
Lady Jiang Ai,

22:36.340 --> 22:37.300
I'll leave the memorials

22:37.300 --> 22:38.260
to you for now.

22:44.950 --> 22:45.910
The bleeding won't stop.

22:48.150 --> 22:49.020
The blood is dark.

22:49.130 --> 22:50.516
- Quick!
- The arrow is poisoned.

22:51.820 --> 22:52.950
What are we to do now?

23:00.230 --> 23:01.260
It won't stop.

23:02.540 --> 23:04.540
Marshal Duan is still unconscious.

23:08.190 --> 23:09.340
Quick!

23:11.430 --> 23:12.270
Move!

23:12.430 --> 23:13.270
Over here.

23:14.820 --> 23:15.660
The water is here.

23:16.740 --> 23:17.580
Bring more water.

23:18.500 --> 23:19.580
Go fetch more water.

23:20.150 --> 23:20.990
Yes.

23:23.390 --> 23:24.230
Hurry!

23:53.950 --> 23:54.790
The water is here.

23:59.180 --> 24:00.020
Duan Xu.

24:00.020 --> 24:01.100
The bleeding won't stop.

24:02.190 --> 24:03.150
Everyone,

24:03.150 --> 24:03.990
step outside first.

24:04.990 --> 24:05.830
This...

24:06.210 --> 24:07.060
Let's go.

24:07.060 --> 24:07.910
Go.

24:07.910 --> 24:08.990
What should we do now?

24:08.990 --> 24:09.830
- Go.
- Let's go.

24:10.190 --> 24:11.430
How do we cure this poison?

24:11.740 --> 24:12.833
I've never seen this poison.

24:18.500 --> 24:19.340
Duan Xu.

24:29.820 --> 24:30.740
Duan Shunxi.

24:39.870 --> 24:40.870
Foxy.

25:04.820 --> 25:05.870
What happened to Duan Xu?

25:06.950 --> 25:08.470
We were ambushed by Chong forces.

25:09.990 --> 25:11.150
Xu and 5,000 riders

25:12.330 --> 25:13.490
were trapped for three days.

25:19.300 --> 25:20.470
Trapped for three days?

25:21.540 --> 25:22.380
Yes.

25:26.060 --> 25:27.100
Has he gone mute?

25:28.060 --> 25:28.910
He was trapped

25:28.910 --> 25:30.083
and never once called for me.

25:41.300 --> 25:42.820
To help the army break free,

25:43.390 --> 25:44.910
Xu led a squad to draw off the enemy.

25:46.060 --> 25:46.900
But an assassin

25:47.190 --> 25:48.500
of the All-Knowing

25:48.500 --> 25:49.340
shot him.

25:50.230 --> 25:51.070
The physician said

25:51.710 --> 25:53.150
he could treat the wound.

25:53.630 --> 25:54.470
But...

25:55.430 --> 25:56.270
But...

25:58.190 --> 25:59.780
The arrow was poisoned.

26:05.060 --> 26:05.950
The physician said

26:07.580 --> 26:09.060
the poison is spreading too fast.

26:10.950 --> 26:12.500
If there is no antidote by tomorrow,

26:14.020 --> 26:15.670
it will seep into Xu's bones.

26:16.713 --> 26:17.773
Then no cure will save him.

26:24.870 --> 26:25.950
Who hurt him?

26:27.390 --> 26:28.340
All I know is it was

26:28.340 --> 26:29.470
the All-Knowing's assassin.

26:30.780 --> 26:31.820
I don't know who it was.

26:38.230 --> 26:39.070
I understand.

26:47.100 --> 26:47.940
Take care of him.

26:49.780 --> 26:50.630
By tomorrow,

26:51.670 --> 26:52.830
I'll bring back the antidote.

27:43.580 --> 27:45.430
You made the poison on the arrow

27:46.260 --> 27:47.230
that struck Duan Xu.

27:49.780 --> 27:50.620
Give me the antidote.

27:53.470 --> 27:55.100
Your Grace, you came in person.

27:56.260 --> 27:58.060
You truly care for Duan Xu.

28:00.100 --> 28:01.390
I've heard that you act

28:01.390 --> 28:02.500
in the Mortal World

28:03.150 --> 28:03.990
with fairness.

28:04.870 --> 28:06.580
You always trade.

28:09.950 --> 28:11.260
What do you want?

28:18.100 --> 28:19.020
The Spirits Lantern.

28:30.430 --> 28:31.870
You know Yan Ke.

28:39.260 --> 28:40.340
I didn't expect

28:41.820 --> 28:43.710
the High Priest of North Chong

28:44.020 --> 28:46.390
to end up like the father he despised

28:47.300 --> 28:48.580
and turn to an evil spirit.

28:51.500 --> 28:53.300
I only wish for North Chong's peace.

28:54.080 --> 28:54.940
I will bear every sin

28:54.950 --> 28:56.260
and every punishment alone.

28:58.230 --> 28:59.500
Duan Xu borrowed

28:59.630 --> 29:01.190
your unmatched power.

29:02.260 --> 29:03.500
He must die.

29:04.540 --> 29:05.380
Or,

29:06.260 --> 29:07.580
you must lose your power.

29:11.020 --> 29:13.190
Do you think Duan Xu has come this far

29:14.100 --> 29:15.670
because I helped him?

29:19.100 --> 29:20.020
Your Grace,

29:21.580 --> 29:22.820
I made the poison.

29:23.710 --> 29:25.870
Only I know the antidote.

29:27.470 --> 29:28.630
You may do as you please.

29:29.521 --> 29:30.568
You may report my dealings

29:30.579 --> 29:32.419
with the evil spirit to the Royal Court.

29:33.630 --> 29:34.990
I will take my life at once.

29:37.759 --> 29:38.858
Without the Spirits Lantern,

29:39.670 --> 29:41.470
I won't give you the antidote.

29:42.710 --> 29:43.910
I may not be a match for you,

29:45.230 --> 29:46.070
but you

29:47.230 --> 29:49.020
can't cut open my mind.

29:51.430 --> 29:52.430
Luda,

29:53.390 --> 29:55.340
you know nothing of war,

29:56.710 --> 29:58.630
so you should never be part of it.

30:00.150 --> 30:01.990
Nor are you fit to be a Priest.

30:03.710 --> 30:05.100
Trying to use Cangshen's ways

30:05.100 --> 30:06.540
to control all under heaven

30:06.990 --> 30:08.990
was foolish from the start.

30:13.470 --> 30:14.780
In this life of yours,

30:15.430 --> 30:16.990
you were never meant for the times

30:18.060 --> 30:19.260
and will achieve nothing.

30:20.260 --> 30:21.100
As for me,

30:22.150 --> 30:24.150
I do share some bond with Duan Xu,

30:24.950 --> 30:26.230
but why would I ever give you

30:26.230 --> 30:27.470
the Spirits Lantern for him?

30:28.150 --> 30:29.100
That thought of yours

30:30.100 --> 30:31.470
is too naive.

30:36.150 --> 30:37.430
You have only one day.

30:39.060 --> 30:40.460
If there's no antidote by tomorrow,

30:41.580 --> 30:42.780
he will die.

30:46.950 --> 30:48.710
Everyone dies eventually.

30:50.540 --> 30:52.100
Whether today or tomorrow,

30:53.500 --> 30:54.670
what difference does it make?

31:14.100 --> 31:14.940
Simu.

31:16.780 --> 31:17.620
Simu.

31:24.390 --> 31:25.230
Simu.

31:27.500 --> 31:28.340
Simu.

31:29.390 --> 31:30.230
Simu.

31:31.540 --> 31:32.430
Simu.

31:32.430 --> 31:33.300
He's calling for me.

31:35.950 --> 31:37.710
Now, he finally calls my name.

31:46.602 --> 31:47.822
(Tomb of He Yicheng and Siwei)

31:47.833 --> 31:49.208
It's been a long time since I came.

31:51.740 --> 31:52.580
Father,

31:54.260 --> 31:55.910
I'll soon avenge you.

32:09.780 --> 32:10.990
I truly don't understand

32:12.230 --> 32:14.500
why Yan Ke wants the Spirits Lantern

32:14.863 --> 32:15.990
and to become the Sovereign.

32:19.190 --> 32:20.950
What is a Sovereign?

32:24.230 --> 32:25.390
Upon the throne,

32:26.190 --> 32:27.540
there is only sacrifice.

32:29.780 --> 32:31.710
But none of those evil spirits

32:33.630 --> 32:35.430
vying for it understands.

32:38.460 --> 32:41.130
♪Lingering for a fleeting moment♪

32:41.990 --> 32:43.260
It's just a sacrifice.

32:46.100 --> 32:47.990
So what if I lose Duan Xu too?

32:50.340 --> 32:51.990
He is only one small part

32:53.190 --> 32:54.910
of all the sacrifices.

32:57.060 --> 32:58.430
Life and death go in cycles.

33:00.500 --> 33:01.430
In this world,

33:03.222 --> 33:04.219
there will be many people

33:04.230 --> 33:05.240
like him.

33:06.500 --> 33:07.340
It is just

33:09.580 --> 33:11.190
that I may have to wait centuries

33:11.190 --> 33:12.820
to meet the next spell bearer.

33:12.840 --> 33:15.880
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

33:17.060 --> 33:18.100
Only a few hundred years.

33:20.990 --> 33:22.060
I can wait that long.

33:23.030 --> 33:28.940
♪Whether I stay or go, I'm all alone♪

33:32.710 --> 33:33.876
The weather is turning cold.

33:37.740 --> 33:38.580
Wake up.

33:40.100 --> 33:41.150
The dream is already over.

33:42.020 --> 33:43.340
I like how you worry about me.

33:46.470 --> 33:48.300
But he is always warm.

33:58.650 --> 34:02.050
♪Falling down like snow♪

34:02.600 --> 34:05.860
♪Joys and sorrows of the mortal world♪

34:06.080 --> 34:09.820
♪Swept along by the daylight♪

34:10.270 --> 34:13.600
♪The forms and hues of the mortal realm♪

34:16.140 --> 34:17.060
I set up a tomb

34:17.060 --> 34:17.910
for you here.

34:17.910 --> 34:21.640
♪Was once touched by laughing tears♪

34:22.060 --> 34:23.750
♪If I could live a simple life♪

34:23.750 --> 34:24.700
But in this world,

34:24.700 --> 34:25.750
you are no longer here.

34:25.750 --> 34:29.430
♪I'd be a guest in a sweet dream♪

34:29.500 --> 34:31.100
I will never find you again.

34:31.100 --> 34:34.580
♪Dawn and dusk rise and set♪

34:34.810 --> 34:36.720
♪Longing to meet, yet parted by destiny♪

34:36.790 --> 34:38.750
It's like no one can hear the words

34:39.870 --> 34:41.700
I'm saying now.

34:43.430 --> 34:44.660
This is what parting

34:47.180 --> 34:48.350
truly means.

34:50.280 --> 34:54.120
♪Accompanied by eternity♪

34:54.870 --> 34:56.020
Duan Xu is no different.

34:59.700 --> 35:00.910
If Duan Xu dies,

35:03.470 --> 35:04.310
in this world,

35:04.310 --> 35:05.790
there will be no more Duan Xu.

35:17.220 --> 35:20.850
♪As stars shift and change places♪

35:20.940 --> 35:22.880
♪A century is like a dream♪

35:22.950 --> 35:24.140
When I had a sense of taste,

35:24.140 --> 35:25.100
I drank this wine.

35:25.100 --> 35:28.330
♪Let me journey across them all♪

35:30.060 --> 35:30.990
It's fine wine.

35:32.720 --> 35:36.270
♪A lone lamp shines on the other shore♪

35:36.270 --> 35:40.080
♪Accompanied by the abyss♪

35:40.270 --> 35:43.190
♪Moments may last♪

35:44.430 --> 35:45.950
Even without the Spirits Lantern,

35:46.750 --> 35:47.750
I can still win.

35:51.950 --> 35:54.020
But you must be disappointed in me.

36:26.950 --> 36:27.790
Simu.

36:29.910 --> 36:31.270
You were trapped for three days.

36:36.340 --> 36:37.180
I just...

36:37.180 --> 36:38.220
A full three days.

36:39.500 --> 36:40.700
Why didn't you ask me for help?

36:43.660 --> 36:45.390
Victory and loss are common in war.

36:47.613 --> 36:48.580
It was not my first time

36:48.580 --> 36:49.580
in grave danger.

36:51.270 --> 36:53.020
If I had to call you every time,

36:54.140 --> 36:55.750
you'd be worn out.

36:58.700 --> 36:59.540
Besides,

37:00.100 --> 37:00.990
even if you came,

37:02.750 --> 37:04.310
you could only save me alone,

37:05.830 --> 37:07.310
at most with Chenying.

37:10.180 --> 37:11.270
As the Marshal,

37:13.310 --> 37:14.950
I could not leave my men behind.

37:30.020 --> 37:30.860
Why?

37:33.350 --> 37:34.310
What did I say wrong?

37:52.870 --> 37:54.060
You said nothing wrong.

37:57.140 --> 37:58.180
Think about it.

37:59.870 --> 38:00.870
You never called for me

38:00.870 --> 38:02.620
when you needed me most.

38:52.750 --> 38:53.590
It hurts.

38:58.430 --> 38:59.910
I'm still badly wounded.

39:17.430 --> 39:18.870
I've pressed on your wound this long,

39:18.870 --> 39:19.963
and only now you feel pain.

39:21.470 --> 39:23.350
When did your senses begin to decay?

39:39.830 --> 39:41.020
A little over five years ago.

39:47.580 --> 39:49.390
Before Yan Ke's rebellion?

39:52.430 --> 39:54.100
Because you gave me your five senses,

39:57.390 --> 39:58.230
right?

40:01.270 --> 40:02.540
Why didn't you tell me?

40:16.220 --> 40:17.750
Mortals are so fragile.

40:22.270 --> 40:23.330
My five senses were keener

40:23.750 --> 40:25.100
than most.

40:26.060 --> 40:27.390
Dulling a little changed nothing.

40:28.803 --> 40:30.176
What sensation do you still desire?

40:31.020 --> 40:32.500
I can exchange it with you now.

40:36.990 --> 40:37.830
No need.

40:43.100 --> 40:44.020
What is not truly mine

40:45.790 --> 40:46.990
will never be mine.

40:59.330 --> 41:02.160
♪I go alone in the night without end♪

41:02.480 --> 41:06.270
♪I can't remember the seasons
or the passing years♪

41:07.390 --> 41:08.580
Let us end things here,

41:10.350 --> 41:11.190
Duan Xu.

41:12.700 --> 41:13.540
What did you say?

41:14.580 --> 41:15.420
Listen.

41:16.180 --> 41:17.310
Let us end things here.

41:17.500 --> 41:18.340
Simu!

41:19.700 --> 41:20.790
Xu, you're awake.

41:21.500 --> 41:22.340
Xu.

41:23.500 --> 41:24.340
Xu, what's wrong?

41:25.500 --> 41:26.750
- Xu.
- Simu!

41:27.790 --> 41:29.110
- Xu.
- Simu!

41:32.790 --> 41:33.630
Simu.

41:33.640 --> 41:37.370
♪I hold a lantern to draw the moon♪

41:37.990 --> 41:39.220
(Liang)
Xu, what's wrong?

41:41.790 --> 41:45.790
♪I have simple wishes, but I fear♪

41:45.790 --> 41:48.830
♪The world can't hold them♪

41:49.050 --> 41:52.290
♪You always stay with me♪

41:52.300 --> 41:53.140
Xu.

41:53.140 --> 41:56.730
♪See the world I've never seen♪

41:59.633 --> 42:00.540
Xu, where do you hurt?

42:00.540 --> 42:01.540
Tell me, Xu.

42:01.540 --> 42:09.220
♪I wish I could live in your heart♪

42:11.350 --> 42:12.750
She's taken back the world

42:17.350 --> 42:18.190
she gave me.

42:30.180 --> 42:31.390
I'll never find her again.

42:32.540 --> 42:33.950
Xu, what are you saying?

42:39.310 --> 42:40.390
Xu, you...

42:47.310 --> 42:48.150
Xu.

42:49.350 --> 42:50.190
Xu.

42:50.660 --> 42:51.500
Xu, what's wrong?

42:52.350 --> 42:53.350
Xu, wake up.

42:53.750 --> 42:54.590
Xu.

42:54.950 --> 42:55.790
Xu.

42:58.720 --> 43:04.050
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:04.380 --> 43:08.630
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:09.990 --> 43:15.360
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:15.660 --> 43:20.260
♪The unbreakable fate♪

43:21.350 --> 43:23.190
♪Suddenly cracked♪

43:35.400 --> 43:40.840
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:41.020 --> 43:45.350
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:46.720 --> 43:52.110
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:52.340 --> 43:56.280
♪The unbreakable fate♪

43:58.050 --> 43:59.940
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:02.600 --> 44:05.760
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

44:05.760 --> 44:08.290
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

44:08.290 --> 44:13.810
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

44:13.810 --> 44:17.050
♪Following fate's guidance♪

44:17.050 --> 44:21.910
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

44:22.250 --> 44:25.270
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

44:25.270 --> 44:28.090
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

44:28.350 --> 44:30.880
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

44:30.880 --> 44:36.300
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

44:36.470 --> 44:39.540
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

44:39.700 --> 44:44.600
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

44:44.810 --> 44:48.280
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
